episodes.title: Inside Scientology in Denver: Church or Cult?
episodes.description:
What’s really inside the Church of Scientology? I visited a real Scientology location, interviewed people on the street, and dug into the most controversial parts of this mysterious organization. From forced disconnection to secret auditing practices — here’s what I found.
